query:
SELECT 
  'client_name' as column_name, COUNT(*) as filled_records FROM crm_clients WHERE client_name IS NOT NULL AND client_name != ''
UNION ALL SELECT 'email', COUNT(*) FROM crm_clients WHERE email IS NOT NULL AND email != ''
UNION ALL SELECT 'phone', COUNT(*) FROM crm_clients WHERE phone IS NOT NULL AND phone != ''
UNION ALL SELECT 'business_type', COUNT(*) FROM crm_clients WHERE business_type IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL SELECT 'status', COUNT(*) FROM crm_clients WHERE status IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL SELECT 'monthly_retainer', COUNT(*) FROM crm_clients WHERE monthly_retainer IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL SELECT 'hourly_rate', COUNT(*) FROM crm_clients WHERE hourly_rate IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL SELECT 'start_date', COUNT(*) FROM crm_clients WHERE start_date IS NOT NULL
UNION ALL SELECT 'notes', COUNT(*) FROM crm_clients WHERE notes IS NOT NULL AND notes != '';
